headline: 3 Reasons LULU Should Be High on Your Watchlist
summary: Lululemon’s 26.7% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 19.4%, and its stock price has climbed to $382.30 per share. This was partly thanks to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
